# VCE HHD Study Website - Low-Fidelity Wireframes

These wireframes outline the basic structure and layout for key page templates of the HHD Study Website. They focus on information hierarchy and element placement, not detailed visual design.

---

## 1. Homepage (`/#home`)

**Purpose:** Welcome users, briefly introduce the site, and provide clear calls to action.

```
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Header                                                      |
| [HHD Hub Logo]   [Home | Unit 3 | Unit 4 | Assess | Gloss]  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                              |
|                [Hero Image/Graphic Placeholder]              |
|                                                              |
|                Welcome to HHD Study Hub!                     |
|                Brief site introduction...                    |
|                                                              |
|                [Button: Explore Unit 3]                      |
|                [Button: View Assessment Prep (Optional)]     |
|                                                              |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Main Content Area ("Glossy Bubble")                          |
|  +--------------------------------------------------------+  |
|  |  Key Features / What We Offer                         |  |
|  |  [Icon] Study Notes   [Icon] Practice Qs   [Icon] Gloss|  |
|  +--------------------------------------------------------+  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Footer                                                      |
|   © Year HHD Hub. Disclaimer...                             |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
```

**Key Elements:**
- **Header:** Consistent across all pages. Logo and primary navigation.
- **Hero Section:** Engaging visual (placeholder), main heading, and introductory paragraph.
- **Call to Action (CTA):** Prominent button(s) directing users to key content (e.g., Unit 3).
- **Main Content Area:** "Glossy bubble" style, optional section highlighting key features or quick links.
- **Footer:** Copyright and disclaimer.

---

## 2. Unit Page (e.g., `/#unit3`)

**Purpose:** Display detailed content for a specific Unit, broken down by Area of Study (AOS) and Key Knowledge points. This will be a long-scrolling page.

```
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Header                                                      |
| [HHD Hub Logo]   [Home | Unit 3 | Unit 4 | Assess | Gloss]  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Main Content Area ("Glossy Bubble")                          |
|  +--------------------------------------------------------+  |
|  |  Unit X: [Unit Title]                                 |  |
|  |  Brief overview of the Unit...                        |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  Area of Study 1: [AOS1 Title]                       |  |
|  |  Introduction to AOS1...                             |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  Key Knowledge Point 1.1                             |  |
|  |  Detailed content for KK 1.1...                      |  |
|  |  [Placeholder for diagrams/tables/images]             |  |
|  |  [Placeholder for interactive element (optional)]     |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  ... (repeat for all KK points in AOS1) ...           |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  Area of Study 2: [AOS2 Title]                       |  |
|  |  Introduction to AOS2...                             |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  Key Knowledge Point 2.1                             |  |
|  |  Detailed content for KK 2.1...                      |  |
|  |  ... (repeat for all KK points in AOS2) ...           |  |
|  +--------------------------------------------------------+  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Footer                                                      |
|   © Year HHD Hub. Disclaimer...                             |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
```

**Key Elements:**
- **Header & Footer:** Consistent.
- **Main Content Area ("Glossy Bubble")**
    - Unit Title & Overview
    - AOS Sections: Each Area of Study with its own title and introduction
    - Key Knowledge Sub-sections: Each with heading, detailed text, placeholders for visuals/interactive elements
    - Horizontal Rule (`<hr>`) to separate major sub-topics

---

## 3. Assessment Prep Page (`/#assessment-prep`)

**Purpose:** Provide guidance and resources for SACs and exams.

```
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Header                                                      |
| [HHD Hub Logo]   [Home | Unit 3 | Unit 4 | Assess | Gloss]  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Main Content Area ("Glossy Bubble")                          |
|  +--------------------------------------------------------+  |
|  |  Assessment Preparation                              |  |
|  |  Overview of assessment in VCE HHD...                |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  School-Assessed Coursework (SACs)                   |  |
|  |  Explanation of SACs, task types...                  |  |
|  |  [Link/Section: Unit 3 SAC Prep]                     |  |
|  |  [Link/Section: Unit 4 SAC Prep]                     |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  End-of-Year Examination                             |  |
|  |  Exam structure, tips, command words...              |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  Study Strategies & Tips                             |  |
|  |  General advice for studying HHD...                  |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  [Placeholder: Practice Questions Section/Link]       |  |
|  +--------------------------------------------------------+  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Footer                                                      |
|   © Year HHD Hub. Disclaimer...                             |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
```

**Key Elements:**
- **Header & Footer:** Consistent.
- **Main Content Area ("Glossy Bubble")**
    - Main heading and introduction
    - Sections for SACs, Exam Prep, Study Strategies
    - Placeholders for links to more detailed pages or practice questions

---

## 4. Glossary Page (`/#glossary`)

**Purpose:** Provide definitions for key HHD terms.

```
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Header                                                      |
| [HHD Hub Logo]   [Home | Unit 3 | Unit 4 | Assess | Gloss]  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Main Content Area ("Glossy Bubble")                          |
|  +--------------------------------------------------------+  |
|  |  Glossary                                            |  |
|  |  Introduction to the glossary...                     |  |
|  |  [Search Bar Placeholder (Optional)]                 |  |
|  |  [A-Z Filter Placeholder (Optional)]                 |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  A                                                  |  |
|  |    Term 1: Definition...                            |  |
|  |    Term 2: Definition...                            |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  B                                                  |  |
|  |    Term 3: Definition...                            |  |
|  |    ... (Alphabetical listing of terms) ...           |  |
|  |                                                      |  |
|  |  Alternative layout: Grid/Card style for terms       |  |
|  |    [Term Card] [Term Card] [Term Card]              |  |
|  |    [Term Card] [Term Card] [Term Card]              |  |
|  +--------------------------------------------------------+  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| Footer                                                      |
|   © Year HHD Hub. Disclaimer...                             |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
```

**Key Elements:**
- **Header & Footer:** Consistent.
- **Main Content Area ("Glossy Bubble")**
    - Main heading
    - Optional search or filter functionality
    - Terms listed alphabetically or in a grid/card layout

